Description: The main purpose of this package is to propose a transparent methodological framework to compare bioregionalisation methods based on hierarchical clustering algorithms, non-hierarchical clustering algorithms or network algorithms as in Lenormand et al. (2020) <doi:10.1002/ece3.4718>.
